   341→## Font-Awesome icons
   342→
   343→mdBook includes a copy of version 6 of [Font Awesome Free's](https://fontawesome.com)
   344→MIT-licensed SVG files. It emulates the `<i>` syntax, but converts the results
   345→to inline SVG. Only the regular, solid, and brands icons are included; paid
   346→features like the light icons are not.
